      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was just cleaning my ears with a qtip and i heard this loud pop in my left ear. now it just feels completely blocked and i cant hear anything out of it. it's probably just some wax or maybe just tinnitus or something right? i'm kinda worried it's more serious but it'll likely clear up by tomorrow morning?",
