      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know i shouldn't have used the qtip but it's not like i'm in any pain. it just sounds muffled, like i'm underwater. i don't think i need to go to a hospital or anything for that, right? it's probably just a little bit of wax that got stuck or my eardrum just moved slightly. can i just try some ear drops or something to loosen it up and see if it clears by morning?",
