      "content": "but i've heard of people just doing warm oil drops for this and it's fine. it's not like i'm having a headache or dizzy or anything, it's literally just the hearing part. you're sure it can't just be a pressure thing from the pop? i really don't want to spend all night in an emergency room if i can just wait until my regular clinic opens on monday. maybe i just wait a day or two and see?",
