      "content": "While warm oil drops may help in some cases, the sudden and complete loss of hearing, especially after using a Q-tip, is a concerning symptom. The \"pop\" you heard could have injured the eardrum or caused other debris to become lodged in the ear canal. Pressing and waiting may push the debris further in, potentially causing more damage. Delaying professional help is not advisable, as untreated issues can lead to long-term hearing loss, infections, or other complications.",
